<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister Critical of Russia's Threat to Latvia </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1201113794 Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network in Finnish 
1100 GMT 12 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1201113794 </F>
<F P=104>  Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Finnish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Swedish Foreign Minister Margaretha Af Ugglas has 
severely criticized Russia for threatening Latvia. Last Monday 
[10 January], Russia placed units of its border troops on alert 
after two Russian generals were arrested in Latvia. According 
to the Swedish foreign minister, such actions violate the 
principles of the CSCE, and are unacceptable. 

</TEXT>

