<H3> <TI>   Nationalist Action Party Official Murdered </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA1301163894 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1600 
GMT 13 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1301163894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Text] Ibrahim Faysal Sakar, the Nationalist Action Party 
chief official for Bodrum District, has been killed. The body 
was found in his house today. He was killed with a knife. His 
car was found dumped off the road near the Gullu crossroads. 
Officials report that a multifaceted investigation is under way 
in connection with the murder. 

