  [Excerpts] Vienna, Jan 17 (AFP) -- Talks resumed Monday 
[17 January] between the International Atomic Energy Agency 
[IAEA] and North Korea over allowing inspections of nuclear 
sites, with Pyongyang officials continuing to refuse permission, 
an IAEA spokesman said. 
