<H3> <TI>   Several Injured in Arson Attack on Ludwigshafen Hostel </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1401121394 Berlin N-TV in German 1100 GMT 14 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1401121394 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin N-TV </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Several residents were injured during an arson 
attack on an asylum-seekers' hostel in Ludwigshafen last night. 
One woman was taken to hospital suffering from smoke 
inhalation, another suffered serious bruising. A police 
spokesman said that the arsonists carried bulky refuse from the 
street into the hallway of the hostel and set fire to it. A 
34-year-old man from Ludwigshafen has been arrested. 

</TEXT>

