<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ankara, Jan 14 (AA) -- Foreign Minister Hikmet Cetin 
said on Friday [14 January] that Turkey will continue to support 
Georgia to overcome the problems it faced. 
  Cetin told at a meeting with his Georgian counterpart 
Alexandr Chikvaidze that he was happy to see Chikvaidze in 
Turkey. 
  Cetin said during Georgian President and Parliament Speaker 
