Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1701230294 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris France-Info Radio </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Since the killing of Monique Afri, France has 
decided to make more reductions in the staff of its official 
facilities in Algeria. The French Consulate in Algiers did not 
open today, and offices will remain closed until further notice. 
France is studying new procedures for distributing visas. 

</TEXT>

