<H3> <TI>   Government Announces Aid Package to CAR </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1501154394 Paris Radio France International in French 1230 
GMT 15 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1501154394 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio France International </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] France has granted the Central African Republic 1.7 
billion CFA francs, that is 17 million francs, to pay the wages 
of public sector workers for one month. Paris stressed that 
this aid is a one-time only action. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-58610 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drweu011_i_94007" </HT>


